# Project Guidelines (pointer)

Canonical guidance: `@rules/core/code-quality-guidelines.mdc`.

**Project-specific:**

- App Router: Server Components by default; `'use client'` only when needed. Route handlers must be thin (validate, call service, return). See `@rules/core/boundaries.mdc`.
- Quality gate: run the project check script after meaningful changes (e.g. `pnpm run check`, `npm run check`).
